'''Munakata Shrine''' (宗像神社, Munakata-jinja) is a {{ill|Shinto shrine|ja|神社|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shinto shrine|qq=}} located in {{ill|Shiroi|ja|白井市|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shiroi|qq=}}, {{ill|Chiba Prefecture|ja|千葉県|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Chiba Prefecture|qq=}}, in the {{ill|Kiyoto|ja|清戸|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kiyoto|qq=}} district.

== Enshrined Deities ==
* {{ill|Three Munakata Goddesses|ja|宗像三女神|1=Three Munakata Goddesses|1=Three Munakata Goddesses|qq=Three Munakata Goddesses|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Three Munakata Goddesses|13=User:Immanuelle/Three Munakata Goddesses|qq=}}
